OL,7,FStormont is under pressure to fund a
OL,8,Fnow two-year-old autism strategy,
OL,9,Fwhich would see early intervention
OL,10,Fservices, support for adults and a
OL,11,Ftraining programme for Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FThe Autism Amendment Act 2022 also
OL,15,Fsets out the need for measurable
OL,16,Ftargets and an independent scrutiny
OL,17,Fbody, which is yet to be recruited for.
