OL,7,FThe political impasse stalled progress
OL,8,Fbut as families mark Autism Awareness
OL,9,FWeek, calls have resurfaced to
OL,10,Fproperly fund the strategy.
OL,12,FChief Executive of Autism NI, Kerry
OL,13,FBoyd, told UTV: "Autistic children and
OL,14,Fadults can't wait any longer. We had
OL,15,Fan Act back in 2011... then we amended
OL,16,Fthat in 2022 to strengthen that and
OL,17,Fnow this strategy has been developed
OL,18,Ffrom that.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/7
