OL,3,CBelfast girl says autism is her
OL,4,C'superpower' as charity calls to fund
OL,5,Cstrategy
OL,7,F"There is a role for an autism
OL,8,Freviewer, which still at the minute
OL,9,Fhasn't been recruited for, but once
OL,10,Fthat happens they will be overseeing
OL,11,Fthe new strategy and we hope that
OL,12,Fwhoever that is ensures that this
OL,13,Fstrategy is rolled out as it should
OL,14,Fbe."
OL,16,FIsla McManus, who's 10 years old, is
OL,17,Fdiagnosed with autism and says it's
OL,18,Fher "wee superpower".
