OL,7,FThe Belfast girl's family are marking
OL,8,FAutism Awareness Week this year by
OL,9,Fsharing that no two children with
OL,10,Fautism are the same and that society
OL,11,Fneeds to work on acceptance of others
OL,12,Fand their needs.
