OL,7,FIn response to Autism NI, a
OL,8,Fspokesperson from the Department of
OL,9,FHealth said: "The Department published
OL,10,Fthe cross-departmental Autism Strategy
OL,11,F2023-2028 in December 2023. The
OL,12,FStrategy sets out the key commitments
OL,13,Fand actions needed to enhance and
OL,14,Fimprove support for autistic people
OL,15,Fand their families.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/7
