OL,7,F"The Department has also published an
OL,8,Finitial two-year Delivery Plan which
OL,9,Fsets out timescales for implementation
OL,10,Fof the actions contained within the
OL,11,FStrategy, many of which are underway,
OL,12,Fin a managed and sustainable way,
OL,13,Ftaking account of the challenging
OL,14,Ffinancial context.
OL,16,F"The actions have been informed
OL,17,Fthrough extensive stakeholder
OL,18,Fengagement and progress will be
OL,19,Fmonitored and reviewed on an annual
OL,20,Fbasis."
